This application for breakfast order with the descriptions of the screenshot
bellows.
This app is the enhanced version of the previous lunch menu, with additional
manipulations to the drop-down menu, the display of literal discount of employee
and military of 25% and 15.35% subsequently, the validation of making sure the
selection of a relative item at the drop-down menu is selected, and the text of the
group box of the drop-down menu must be changed accordingly to the selection
of the [Main Item], for instance, it shows [House Authentic Omelets] on top of the
drop-down menu if the “House Authentic Omelets” is checked and so forth (see
the screenshot for details).
The first time the app runs, the menu displays with default setting.
